{"componentChunkName":"component---src-components-markdown-js","path":"/support/migrating-to-recipe-12","result":{"data":{"page":{"parent":{"__typename":"File","id":"b6291dd2-2280-573e-ac13-a29a536ac008","name":"migrating-to-recipe-12"},"htmlAst":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"ul","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#prologue"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Prologue"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#breaking-changes"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Breaking changes"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#migration-steps"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Migration steps"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ul","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#installation"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Installation"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#ie-11-support"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"IE 11 support"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#build-tooling"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Build tooling"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#server-rendering"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Server rendering"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"prologue","style":"position:relative;"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#prologue","ariaLabel":"prologue permalink","className":["anchor","before"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"Prologue"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"When the Recipe project was created, we had to decide how we would package styles alongside React components for distribution within our applications. Ideally styles would be co-located and packaged with components, such that applications could use Recipe components without having to \"remember\" to manually include a separate stylesheet-per-component, or maintain a large global stylesheet."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The Recipe team made the choice to utilize the "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://emotion.sh/docs/introduction"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"emotion"}]},{"type":"text","value":" css-in-js library, as it had already been well established as a tooling choice in ezcater's core web sites and web applications. Using emotion within Recipe solved the packaging and distribution problem, without requiring any additional configuration overhead for our existing applications."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"In 2019, the Emotion maintainers shipped a major release of the emotion libraries (v10), adding some very useful new features and updating the internals for compatibility with React (by removing usage of deprecated APIs). Unfortunately for us as consumers of Emotion, this change required a significant update to Recipe that needed tight coordination with downstream applications. "}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Updating any major peer-dependency is somewhat challenging, and this situation was no different; applications could not upgrade Emotion without a corresponding Recipe release, but Recipe couldn't be upgraded without either cutting off support for applications that were not yet using the latest version of Emotion. üêî ü•ö"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Once again, we find ourselves in a similar situation - the Emotion team have shipped a major release with breaking changes (v11), and progress in the react tooling ecosystem (supporting webpack 5) necessitates that we discontinue use of the prior version for compatibility."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"This leaves us two options, upgrade emotion in Recipe (and all downstream applications), or remove Recipe's dependency on Emotion to unblock downstream applications from their own upgrades."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The Recipe team have chosen to do the latter. We've chosen a strategy that creates with some new opportunities: "}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ul","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Solving the \"Recipe theming\" story for supporting multiple applications with different branding/marketing focuses"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Enabling a solid story for creating new \"branded\" components outside of Recipe by utilizing Recipe's theming engine"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Reducing runtime overhead by leveraging static CSS, instead of CSS generated at runtime"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Providing a path to optimizing performance by leveraging the extraction of CSS at build-time"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Creating a developer-friendly experience by leveraging TypeScript at the core our our styling engine (to name just a few)."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The Recipe v12 release is the first step of this journey."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"hr","properties":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"breaking-changes","style":"position:relative;"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#breaking-changes","ariaLabel":"breaking changes permalink","className":["anchor","before"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"Breaking changes"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"This release is a "},{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"major version release"}]},{"type":"text","value":" and as such, "},{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"will require migration steps"}]},{"type":"text","value":" for applications that currently use Recipe version 11.x or below."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"While we have tried to minimize the number of major API changes, the following changes are considered breaking changes:"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ol","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"While all components that accept a "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"className"}]},{"type":"text","value":" prop in v11 will continue to accept a "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"className"}]},{"type":"text","value":" prop in v12, new specificity issues may occur if both the "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"className"}]},{"type":"text","value":" provided is generated by emotion AND the associate styles override Recipe's component styles."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The CSS variable names Recipe uses within its components have changed. While the Recipe's CSS variable names are "},{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"not considered part of Recipe's stable/documented public API"}]},{"type":"text","value":", as these variable are visible with devtools we feel it is important to call out that the naming convention we use internally has changed."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The v1 version of the "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"@recipe-ui/theme-marketplace"}]},{"type":"text","value":" package is not compatible with Recipe v12 (due to breaking change #2)."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Other significant changes that are considered non-breaking include:"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ol","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"/recipe/components/EzTable"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"EzTable"}]},{"type":"text","value":" component no longer pins the first column on small screens."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"hr","properties":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"migration-steps","style":"position:relative;"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#migration-steps","ariaLabel":"migration steps permalink","className":["anchor","before"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"Migration steps"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{"id":"installation","style":"position:relative;"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#installation","ariaLabel":"installation permalink","className":["anchor","before"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"Installation"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"You can update your Recipe installation using a package manager like "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://docs.npmjs.com/cli/v6/commands/npm"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"npm"}]},{"type":"text","value":" or "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://classic.yarnpkg.com/lang/en/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"yarn"}]},{"type":"text","value":"."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"pre","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{"className":["language-term"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"npm install @ezcater/recipe@latest\n---\nor\n---\nyarn upgrade @ezcater/recipe@latest\n"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"If you're building a marketplace application, you will also need install the latest marketplace theme as follows:"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"pre","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{"className":["language-term"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"npm install @recipe-ui/theme-marketplace@latest\n---\nor\n---\nyarn add @recipe-ui/theme-marketplace@latest\n"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"br","properties":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{"id":"ie-11-support","style":"position:relative;"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#ie-11-support","ariaLabel":"ie 11 support permalink","className":["anchor","before"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"IE 11 support"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Applications that need to support IE11 may require an updated list of polyfills to use Recipe."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The Recipe team recommend using "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://polyfill.io/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Polyfill.io"}]},{"type":"text","value":" in your application. Polyfill.io will apply only the polyfills needed for the requesting browser."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"We recommend using the following "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://polyfill.io/v3/url-builder/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"polyfill bundle"}]},{"type":"text","value":" features:"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ul","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"default"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"es2015"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"es2016"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"es2017"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"smoothscroll"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Reflect.ownKeys"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"NodeList.prototype.forEach"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"If you're using the "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://github.com/jhildenbiddle/css-vars-ponyfill"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"css-vars-ponyfill"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":" to provide support for CSS variables in IE, please ensure you're running an up-to-date release. Version "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://github.com/jhildenbiddle/css-vars-ponyfill/blob/master/CHANGELOG.md#240"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2.4.0"}]},{"type":"text","value":" or higher is needed for compatibility with Recipe."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"br","properties":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{"id":"build-tooling","style":"position:relative;"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#build-tooling","ariaLabel":"build tooling permalink","className":["anchor","before"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"Build tooling"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Recipe v11 internally used "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://github.com